37-1446-8 |url=https://archive.org/details/june194400will }}\n* {{Cite web |url=https://www.pbs.org/thewar/detail_5211.htm |work=The War |title=North Africa (1940\u20131943) |first=David T. |last=Zabecki |year=2007 |publisher=PBS |accessdate=8 September 2010}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons|North African campaign}}\n* [http://www1.yadvashem.org/yv/en/education/newsletter/25/index.asp?WT.mc_id=wiki The Jews of North Africa and the Holocaust] an e-Newsletter for Holocaust educators by [[Yad Vashem]]\n* [https://www.bbc.co.uk/history/worldwars/wwtwo/launch_ani_north_africa_campaign.shtml BBC's flash video of the North African campaign]\n* [http://www.worldwar-2.net/timelines/war-in-the-desert/war-in-the-desert-index-1940.htm Timeline of the North African campaign]\n* General sites on the North African campaign\n** [http://www.spartacus-educational.com/2WWdesert.htm Spartacus Educational website: Desert War]\n** {{Cite web |first=Paul |last=John |url=http://www.topedge.com/panels/ww2/na/noframe.html |title=World War II Study \u2013 Case Study North Africa |year=1997}}\n** {{Cite web |first=David T. |last=Zabecki |title=Battlefield North Africa: Rommel's Rise And Fall |work=Military.com World War II |year=2000 |url=http://www.military.com/Content/MoreContent?file=PRnafrica}}\n* [http://www.warmuseum.ca/cwm/exhibitions/newspapers/operations/northafrican_e.shtml Canadian World War 2 Online Newspaper Archives \u2013 The North African Campaigns, 1940\u20131943]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20120828133551/http://desertwar.net/north-african-campaign.html North African Campaign Desert War.net]\n\n{{World War II}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2019}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:North African Campaign| ]]\n[[Category:African theatres of World War II|.]]\n[[Category:Campaigns of World War II]]\n[[Category:Western Desert Campaign]]\n[[Category:Tunisian Campaign]]\n[[Category:Egypt in World War II]]\n[[Category:Libya in World War II]]\n[[Category:Conflicts in 1940]]\n[[