ring clubs and [[Narrow gauge railways of New Zealand|narrow gauge railways]].\n\n===North Island===\n;[[Northland Region|Northland]]\n\n*[[Bay of Islands Vintage Railway|Bay of Islands Vintage Railway Charitable Trust]]\n*Whangarei Steam & Model Railway Club\n*Whangarei Model Engineering Club\n\n;[[Auckland]]\n*[http://www.mainlinesteam.co.nz/ Mainline Steam]\n*[[Glenbrook Vintage Railway]]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20060511191155/http://www.railfan.org.nz/ Railway Enthusiasts Society]\n*[http://www.waitakeretramline.org.nz/ The Waitakere Tramline Society]\n*[http://www.watercare.co.nz/default,recreation.sm Watercare Services]\n*[http://www.motat.org.nz/ Western Springs Railway] [[Museum of Transport and Technology]]\n*[http://www.motat.org.nz/ Western Springs Tramway] [[Museum of Transport and Technology]]\n*[http://www.rail.co.nz/ Whangaparaoa Narrow Gauge Railway]\n*Auckland Society of Model Engineers Incorporated\n*Manukau Live Steamers\n\n;[[Waikato]] / [[Coromandel, New Zealand|Coromandel]]\n*[http://www.bushtramwayclub.com/ Bush Tramway Club]\n*[[NZR DF class (1954)|DF]] 1501 Restoration Charitable Trust\n*[[Driving Creek Railway]]\n*[[Goldfields Railway]]\n*Victoria Battery Tramway Society\n*Te Aroha Mountain Railway\n*Thames Small Gauge Railway Society\n*Hamilton Model Engineers\n*Cambridge Model Engineering Society Inc\n*Waihi Small Gauge Railway\n\n;[[Bay of Plenty]]\n\n*Rotorua - Ngongotaha Rail Trust\n*[[Geyserland Express]] Trust\n*Tauranga Model Marine and Engineering Club\n*Eastern Bay of Plenty Model Engineering Society\n\n;[[East Cape]] / [[Hawke's Bay (region)|Hawke's Bay]]\n\n*East Coast Museum of Technology\n*[https://www.gcvr.org.nz/ Gisborne City Vintage Railway Inc]\n*Hawkes Bay Steam Society\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20080525165110/http://www.geocities.com/ormondvillerail/  Ormondville Rail Preservation Group]\n*Hawkes Bay Model Engineering Society\n*Havelock North Live Steamers & Associates\n\n;[[Taranaki Region|Taranaki]]\n*[htt